#META# Type: Translation
#META# Translator: Ḥunayn ibn Isḥāq
#META# Translated from: Syriac (close)
#META# Date: between 825 and 873
#META# Ed_info: Lyons, Malcolm C. (1966), Kitāb tadbīr al-amrāḍ al-ḥādda li-Buqrāṭ (Hippocrates :: Regimen in acute diseases) (Arabic Technical and Scientific Texts 1), W. Heffer and Sons, Cambridge, vol. 1, pp. 1-44

